26 #pragma once
27 
28 #include "ThreadGlobalData.h"
29 #include <wtf/text/AtomicString.h>
30 
31 namespace WebCore {
32 
33 struct CachedResourceRequestInitiators {
34     CachedResourceRequestInitiators();
35 
36     const AtomicString css;
37     const AtomicString eventsource;
38     const AtomicString fetch;
39     const AtomicString icon;
40     const AtomicString xmlhttprequest;
41     WTF_MAKE_NONCOPYABLE(CachedResourceRequestInitiators); WTF_MAKE_FAST_ALLOCATED;
42 private:
43     friend class ThreadGlobalData;
44 };
45 
46 inline const CachedResourceRequestInitiators& cachedResourceRequestInitiators()
47 {
48     return threadGlobalData().cachedResourceRequestInitiators();
49 }
50 
51 } // namespace WebCore
